method.description:
Returns a [Dictionary] mapping preset (patch) numbers ([int]) to instrument names ([String]) for the given bank number. Use bank [code]0[/code] for General MIDI melodic instruments, or bank [code]128[/code] for General MIDI percussion.
Only presets that exist in the loaded SoundFont are included. Preset numbers range from 0 to 127.
[codeblock]
var sf2 : SoundFont2 = load("res://gm.sf2")
var instruments = sf2.get_preset_list(0)
for patch in instruments:
    print("Patch %d: %s" % [patch, instruments[patch]])
[/codeblock]
